thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by L D

author: L D
title: L D
text: Was initially a little concerned reading that the cars were older models but we had a nearly new vehicle that got us all around the country and back with no trouble. The customer service from the online reservations to all my questions to picking up and returning the vehicle were top notch: friendly and efficient. The staff went over and above. With the best prices around, I would definitely recommend Omega!
